English football club Chelsea to face Brazil's Corinthians in the 2012 FIFA Club World Cup final on 16 December, after 3–1 win over Mexican club Monterrey in the semifinal. (FIFA) (ESPN) (The Guardian)A report alleges that Ed T. Rush, head of men's basketball officiating for the Pac-12 Conference, offered $5,000 or a trip to Cancún to any referee who would call a technical foul against or eject Arizona Wildcats head coach Sean Miller during the 2013 Pac-12 Conference Men's Basketball Tournament. (CBS Sports)